'''大豆配方'''，也称'''大豆配方奶'''，是[[母乳|母乳]]的替代品。其配方奶粉以加工过的[[大豆|大豆]]作为[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]来源，通常爲粉状或液態<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK153456/|title=PROMOTING BREASTFEEDING DURING PREGNANCY – STEP 3|first1=National Center for Biotechnology|last1=Information|first2=U. S. National Library of Medicine 8600 Rockville|last2=Pike|first3=Bethesda|last3=MD|first4=20894|last4=Usa|date=2017-08-07|publisher=World Health Organization|accessdate=2017-08-07|via=www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822183222/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK153456/|archivedate=2017-08-22|dead-url=no}}{{PD-notice}}</ref>。大豆配方通常不含[[乳糖|乳糖]]，而含有其他类型糖。但是，对[[乳糖不耐|乳糖蛋白不耐受]]的婴儿也可能对大豆蛋白不耐受。

大豆配方与母乳有很多不同<ref>{{cite book | last = Walker | first = Marsha | title = Breastfeeding management for the clinician : using the evidence | url = https://archive.org/details/breastfeedingman0000walk_u4k6 | publisher = Jones and Bartlett Publishers | location = Sudbury, Mass | year = 2011 | isbn = 9780763766511 }}</ref>。大豆蛋白抑制[[铁|铁]]的吸收，[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]讨论过在大豆配方中添加铁元素以补偿这种影响<ref name=whoanemia>{{cite web | url = https://www.who.int/nutrition/publications/micronutrients/anaemia_iron_deficiency/9241542497.pdf?ua=1 | publisher = The World Health Organization | title = Preventing and Controlling Iron Defiency Anaemia Through Primary Health Care | date = 1990 | accessdate = 2017-08-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170808032740/http://www.jiaci.org/summary/vol27-issue1-num1451 | archivedate = 2017-08-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大豆配方中有天然植物性化合物[[植酸|植酸]]，具有较强的抑制铁吸收能力。尽管植酸在加工中可以被剔除，但目前是否采取这种做法的制造商数据并不齐备。其中[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]和[[越南|越南]]已经对大豆配方奶粉进行了规范，要求配方中包括[[乙二胺四乙酸|乙二胺四乙酸]]，以增强婴儿对铁的吸收。含有强化铁的大豆配方中，通常对铁化合物进行处理，以防止配方奶粉变黑<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.who.int/nutrition/publications/guide_food_fortification_micronutrients.pdf?ua=1 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2017-08-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808032740/http://www.jiaci.org/summary/vol27-issue1-num1451 |archivedate=2017-08-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==成分==
大豆配方可能存在[[转基因食品争议|转基因大豆问题]]，这种情况可能会降低配方的营养价值<ref name=mwalker>{{cite journal|title=Formula Supplementation of Breastfed Infants: Helpful or Hazardous?|first=Marsha|last=Walker|date=2015-08-01|journal={{tsl|en|ICAN: Infant, Child, & Adolescent Nutrition||ICAN: Infant, Child, & Adolescent Nutrition}}|volume=7|issue=4|pages=198–207|doi=10.1177/1941406415591208|}}</ref>。以大豆为基础的大豆配方奶粉可能含有[[铝|铝]]、植物酸盐和植物雌激素（[[異黃酮|異黃酮]]），这些物质可能会产生意外效果。其他配方有[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]，如[[牛磺酸|牛磺酸]]、[[蛋氨酸|蛋氨酸]]和[[肉碱|肉碱]]。添加的矿物质有[[磷|磷]]、[[钙|钙]]、铁和[[锌|锌]]。

==适应症==
[[母乳喂养|母乳喂养]]仍然是喂养婴儿的首选方案<ref>{{cite journal|title=Soy infant formula: is it that bad?|first1=Yvan|last1=Vandenplas|first2=Elisabeth|last2=De Greef|first3=Thierry|last3=Devreker|first4=Bruno|last4=Hauser|date=2011-02-01|journal=Acta Paediatrica|volume=100|issue=2|pages=162–166|doi=10.1111/j.1651-2227.2010.02021.x|pmid = 20860705}}</ref>。当母乳喂养无法实现时，配方奶可以起到替代作用<ref name= mwalker/>。使用大豆配方所产生的适应症有[[半乳糖血症|半乳糖血症]]和{{le|乳糖酶缺乏症|lactase deficiency}}。当儿童对牛奶出现过敏时，可以使用大豆配方，它通常较其他母乳配方用品更便宜<ref name=yvan>{{cite journal|title=Soy infant formula: is it that bad?|first1=Yvan|last1=Vandenplas|first2=Elisabeth|last2=De Greef|first3=Thierry|last3=Devreker|first4=Bruno|last4=Hauser|date=2011-02-01|journal=Acta Paediatrica|volume=100|issue=2|pages=162–166|doi=10.1111/j.1651-2227.2010.02021.x|pmid=20860705}}</ref>。

==使用==
曾经有关于大豆配方的报道称，大豆配方成分可能会影响儿童的生殖功能。但是研究显示大豆配方使用与生殖系统功能异常并不存在相关性<ref>{{cite journal|title=Compared with Feeding Infants Breast Milk or Cow-Milk Formula, Soy Formula Feeding Does Not Affect Subsequent Reproductive Organ Size at 5 Years of Age|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-nutrition_2015-05_145_5/page/871|first1=Aline|last1=Andres|first2=Mary B.|last2=Moore|first3=Leann E.|last3=Linam|first4=Patrick H.|last4=Casey|first5=Mario A.|last5=Cleves|first6=Thomas M.|last6=Badger|date=2015-05-01|journal=The Journal of Nutrition|volume=145|issue=5|pages=871–875|doi=10.3945/jn.114.206201|pmid=25761499|}}</ref>。大豆配方奶粉的使用有一百多年的历史<ref name= mwalker/>，最早使用的历史可追溯到1909年<ref name = yvan/>。

==过敏及其他问题==
大豆配方奶粉存在{{le|儿童过敏|Allergies in children|过敏问题}}<ref>{{cite journal|title=Non–IgE-mediated gastrointestinal food allergy|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-allergy-and-clinical-immunology_2015-05_135_5/page/1114|first1=Anna|last1=Nowak-Węgrzyn|first2=Yitzhak|last2=Katz|first3=Sam Soheil|last3=Mehr|first4=Sibylle|last4=Koletzko|date=2015-05-01|journal=Journal of Allergy and Clinical Immunology|volume=135|issue=5|pages=1114–1124|doi=10.1016/j.jaci.2015.03.025|pmid=25956013}}</ref>。报道显示一些在三个月以下的婴儿在使用大豆配方后出现慢性食物蛋白引起的[[小肠结肠炎|小肠结肠炎]]综合征（{{lang|en|FPIES}}）<ref name="Nowak-WęgrzynJarocka-Cyrta2017">{{cite journal|last1=Nowak-Węgrzyn|first1=A|last2=Jarocka-Cyrta|first2=E|last3=Moschione Castro|first3=APB|title=Food Protein–Induced Enterocolitis Syndrome|journal=Journal of Investigational Allergology and Clinical Immunology|volume=27|issue=1|year=2017|pages=1–18|issn=1018-9068|doi=10.18176/jiaci.0135|pmid=28211341|}}</ref>。[[法国|法国]]已经停止在超市销售大豆为基础的配方奶粉。在美国，大豆配方奶粉占该国配方奶市场的20%；在新西兰为10%；在比利时和英国为5%<ref name =yvan/>。

